Package nl.b3p.tailormap.api.geotools.wfs

Class SimpleWFSHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.b3p.tailormap.api.geotools.wfs.SimpleWFSHelper
  • public class SimpleWFSHelper
extends Object
    Lightweight WFS client helper with a fault-tolerant 'be liberal in what you accept' design - no complete WFS XML mapping for capabilities and XML feature type schemas such as the heavyweight GeoTools WFS DataStore.

      • getOutputFormats

        public static List<String> getOutputFormats​(String wfsUrl,
                                            String typeName,
                                            String username,
                                            String password)
                                     throws Exception
        Just get the list of supported output formats for the typename. If there are no specific output formats for the type, the generally supported output formats are returned. Requests WFS 1.1.0 but also handles WFS 2.0.0 responses.
        Throws:
        Exception
